### Mobile POS API Test Suite (REST Client / HTTP File)
### 💡 ວິທີໃຊ້: ຕິດຕັ້ງສ່ວນເສີມ "REST Client" ໃນ VS Code ແລ້ວກົດ "Send Request" ຢູ່ເທິງຫົວແຕ່ລະ API ໄດ້ເລີຍ!

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### ປ່ຽນຄ່າ Token ດ້ານລຸ່ມນີ້ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ Login ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ
@authToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.data.token}}

# ==============================================================================
# 1. ລະບົບ Authentication & Users
# ==============================================================================

### 🔑 1.1 ສະໝັກບັນຊີພະນັກງານ (Register)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "cashier_noi",
  "password": "securepassword999",
  "name": "ນາງ ນ້ອຍ ຄຳມີ",
  "roleId": 3
}

### 🔑 1.2 ເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບ (Login ບັນຊີ Admin)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 🔑 1.3 ເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບ (Login ບັນຊີພະນັກງານທີ່ຫາກໍສະໝັກ)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "cashier_noi",
  "password": "securepassword999"
}

### 👥 1.4 ດຶງຂໍ້ມູນພະນັກງານທັງໝົດ (🔒 Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 👥 1.5 ດຶງຂໍ້ມູນພະນັກງານດ້ວຍ ID (🔒 Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 👥 1.6 ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນພະນັກງານ (🔒 Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ນາງ ນ້ອຍ ຄຳມີ (ແກ້ໄຂແລ້ວ)",
  "roleId": 2
}

### 👥 1.7 ລຶບພະນັກງານ (🔒 Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


# ==============================================================================
# 2. ລະບົບຈັດການ Roles
# ==============================================================================

### 🏷️ 2.1 ສ້າງ Role ໃໝ່ (🔒 Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MANAGER"
}

### 🏷️ 2.2 ດຶງຂໍ້ມູນ Roles ທັງໝົດ (🔒 Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 🏷️ 2.3 ດຶງຂໍ້ມູນ Role ດ້ວຍ ID (🔒 Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 🏷️ 2.4 ແກ້ໄຂ Role (🔒 Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/roles/4
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "SUPERVISOR"
}

### 🏷️ 2.5 ລຶບ Role (🔒 Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/4
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


# ==============================================================================
# 3. ລະບົບໝວດໝູ່ (Categories) & ຍີ່ຫໍ້ (Brands)
# ==============================================================================

### 🗂️ 3.1 ສ້າງໝວດໝູ່ໃໝ່ (🔒 Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tablet"
}

### 🗂️ 3.2 ດຶງໝວດໝູ່ທັງໝົດ (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

### 🏷️ 3.3 ສ້າງຍີ່ຫໍ້ໃໝ່ (🔒 Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/brands
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Apple"
}

### 🏷️ 3.4 ດຶງຍີ່ຫໍ້ທັງໝົດ (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/brands

### 🏷️ 3.5 ດຶງຍີ່ຫໍ້ດ້ວຍ ID (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/brands/1

### 🏷️ 3.6 ແກ້ໄຂຍີ່ຫໍ້ (🔒 Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/brands/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Apple Inc."
}

### 🏷️ 3.7 ລຶບຍີ່ຫໍ້ (🔒 Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/brands/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


# ==============================================================================
# 4. ລະບົບສິນຄ້າ (Products)
# ==============================================================================

### 📦 4.1 ສ້າງສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ພ້ອມຮູບພາບ ແລະ ລາຄາ/ສະຕັອກ (Nested Create - 🔒 Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max",
  "description": "5G, Camera 48MP, Apple A17 Pro Chip",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "brandId": 1,
  "images": {
    "create": [
      {
        "imageUrl": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1695048133142-1a20484d2569?q=80&w=600",
        "isMain": true
      }
    ]
  },
  "variants": {
    "create": [
      {
        "color": "Titanium Black",
        "sku": "IPH15PM-BLK",
        "price": 45000000.00,
        "stockQuantity": 10
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 📦 4.2 ດຶງສິນຄ້າທັງໝົດ (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 📦 4.3 ດຶງສິນຄ້າດ້ວຍ ID (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1

### 📦 4.4 ແກ້ໄຂສິນຄ້າ (🔒 Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max (Updated)",
  "description": "Titanium Body, A17 Pro Chip"
}

### 📦 4.5 ລຶບສິນຄ້າ (🔒 Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


# ==============================================================================
# 5. ລະບົບສະຕັອກ & ຮັບເຄື່ອງເຂົ້າຄັງ (Stocks & IMEI)
# ==============================================================================

### 📥 5.1 ເພີ່ມເລກ IMEI / Serial Number ເຂົ້າສະຕັອກ (🔒 Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/stocks/add
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": 1,
  "serialNumber": "352617283948571"
}

### 🔍 5.2 ຍິງບາໂຄ້ດເຊັກ IMEI / S/N (🔒 Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/check/352617283948571
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ✏️ 5.3 ປັບປຸງສະຖານະ IMEI ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ (🔒 Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/stocks/status/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CLAIM"
}


# ==============================================================================
# 6. ລະບົບລູກຄ້າສະມາຊິກ (Customers)
# ==============================================================================

### 👥 6.1 ລົງທະບຽນລູກຄ້າໃໝ່ (🔒 Auth Required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ທ້າວ ສົມຊາຍ ໃຈດີ",
  "phone": "02055555555"
}

### 👥 6.2 ດຶງຂໍ້ມູນລູກຄ້າທັງໝົດ (🔒 Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 👥 6.3 ຄົ້ນຫາລູກຄ້າດ້ວຍເບີໂທ (🔒 Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers/phone/02055555555
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 🏆 6.4 ປັບປຸງ/ເພີ່ມຄະແນນລູກຄ້າ (🔒 Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/customers/points/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": 100
}

### 🗑️ 6.5 ລຶບຂໍ້ມູນລູກຄ້າ (🔒 Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/customers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


# ==============================================================================
# 7. ລະບົບປິດບິນຂາຍໜ້າ POS (Orders)
# ==============================================================================

### 🛒 7.1 ປິດບິນຂາຍ (POS Checkout) (🔒 Auth Required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "totalAmount": 45000000.00,
  "items": [
    {
      "variantId": 1,
      "quantity": 1,
      "priceAtTime": 45000000.00,
      "stockItemIds": [1]
    }
  ]
}

### 🧾 7.2 ດຶງປະຫວັດບິນຂາຍທັງໝົດ (🔒 Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 🧾 7.3 ດຶງປະຫວັດບິນຂາຍດ້ວຍ ID (🔒 Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ❌ 7.4 ຍົກເລີກບິນຂາຍ (🔒 Admin & Cashier Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/cancel/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
